UPDATE: Three Bodies Recovered From Lagos Collapsed Building
0 Comments
16 Hours Ago First responders from the Lagos State Emergency Management Agency arrived at the scene to begin rescue operations. According to the PRO, the recovered persons from the rubble were two adult males while the "five dead persons were also males". Meanwhile, the Director-General, Lagos State Emergency Management Agency, Dr Olufemi Oke-Osanyintolu said emergency responders recovered the bodies following the deployment of heavy-duty equipment by the agency. He added that the recovery operation was still ongoing in a bid to rescue other victims of the tragedy.